127
00:08:41,786 --> 00:08:43,526
Panebože.

128
00:08:43,526 --> 00:08:46,627
Zdravím, pane.

129
00:08:46,627 --> 00:08:49,026
Mal som sa vám ozvať prvý.

130
00:08:49,026 --> 00:08:50,350
Samozrejme.

131
00:08:51,085 --> 00:08:54,405
Mám pre vás skvelú ponuku.

132
